# Planning Standards

**Spec files**: `specs/feature-[name].md`, `specs/api-[name].md`, `specs/requirements-[name].md`. One concern per file.

**Task format**: Title (verb + object), description, acceptance criteria (testable), dependencies, effort (T-shirt or hours), type (feature/bug/refactor/test/docs/infra).

**Acceptance criteria**: Given/when/then or bullet list. Each item verifiable. No "works correctly" without definition.

**Prioritization**: P0 blockers, P1 core, P2 nice-to-have, P3 polish. Order by value and risk. Unblock dependencies first.
